```lang-js 
import { createStackNavigator } from &#39;react-navigation-stack&#39;;
```
Now, create navigation : 
```lang-js 
const Navigation = createStackNavigator ({
  WeatherDetails: { screen: WeatherDetails },
  CityLists: { screen: CityLists }
});
```
